headline: Citigroup: Post-Earnings Technical Strength Is A Selling Opportunity
summary: Citigroup stock has rallied over 50% in the past year, but I believe it is overvalued relative to its results. See why I rate C stock a sell.

headline: Asian tech fundraising to expand 10% in 2025, says Citi
summary: Citi expects increased momentum in Asian fundraising for tech companies into 2025, driven by developments in artificial intelligence and robust activity in India and Taiwan, the Wall Street bank said...

headline: Dodge & Cox Balanced Fund Q4 2024 Shareholder Letter
summary: The S&P 500 Index rose by 26.3% in 2023 and posted a 25.0% return in 2024, marking its largest consecutive annual gains since 1998. Read more here.
